==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Diametrical
<hw>Di*am"e*tric*al</hw>
<pr>(?)</pr>, }</mhw> <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Of or pertaining to
a diameter.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>As remote as possible, as if at the opposite end of
a diameter; directly adverse.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Diametrically</ent>⟦br⟧
